rubric.description:
This is the first project for students in the Predictive Analyst for Business Nanodegree. The aim for this project is to get students familiar with the reviews process and to help them get their feet wet in predictive analytics. Students will be able to technically write about a business problem and make a recommendation based on their short analysis.

Student Instructions 

After completing the project by filling out the submission template and reviewing it using the [project rubric](https://review.udacity.com/#!/rubrics/463/view), click the Submit Project button below and upload your submission.
